Class CalculatedDataFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Fragment
      • Fragments.CalculatedDataFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class CalculatedDataFragment
extends android.app.Fragment
    Fragment responsible for managing calculated data points. From here, the user can add or edit data points for any given activity. The will have the ability to write expressions based on other variables.
